Hmm, I always imagine Zitravgrad having a grander or a bigger army, though nothing wrong with having a smaller one! ^^;

- The fact that Premier Kazimir I. Miroslavsky has 4 children is also something I just learned, and they are all rather close to each other in terms of age. Must be quite a havoc to take care of all 4 of them. ><

- Premier Kazimir I. Miroslavsky again, that he is a bisexual, which... I am finding out so much today, eh? Once again, there is nothing wrong with bisexuality and by finding out, I was just surprised, that's all! Dude definitely has a few screws loose in his head, but this one I already knew!

- As for Population and Geography, surprising that there are tens of thousands of people living in the R-zones, Radiation Zones, which I am assuming. Kinda reminds me of the people in RL Chernobyl, where they don't really tend to have the amenities and utilities that most normal folks enjoy.
